{"tid":1198130,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蔡英文 ：台灣撐香港 我們守台灣","createTime":"2019-06-10T06:55:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T11:14:33.000Z","uid":171449,"like":61,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5735f60219115f77a7110c64de0d355022a54f9c","tid":1198130,"uid":171449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T06:55:09.000Z","msg":"台灣撐香港 我們守台灣<br />\n  <br />\n重要的國際媒體今天都在報導昨天香港的「反送中」大遊行。全世界關注自由、民主與人權的人，也都非常關注這個大遊行，也都很支持香港人的主張。<br />\n  <br />\n台灣也不例外，我們同樣支持香港人追求自由、民主與人權。自由就像空氣一樣，只會在窒息時，才會察覺它的存在。<br />\n  <br />\n因此，我再次強調，一國兩制對台灣來說，是絕對不能接受的。一旦接受一國兩制，我們就會失去捍衛自由、民主與人權的權利，也會失去選擇自己未來的權利。<br />\n  <br />\n我也要呼籲台灣人民繼續關注香港的發展，一起來撐香港，也一起來保衛台灣。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/tsaiingwen/photos/a.10151242056081065/10155879900406065/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ftsaiingwen%2Fphotos%2Fa.10151242056081065%2F10155879900406065%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=AePTNAtL1N4PdcNq2S6jCHlPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=abe326fa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/tsaiingwen/photos/a.10151242056081065/10155879900406065/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"5cb69229b5ae4172ca26dae0afbe855dbc787ab0","tid":1198130,"uid":144529,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T06:56:52.000Z","msg":"共同敵人中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1079cde25bebbc4a5483a14e45444f9abbbacd1a","tid":1198130,"uid":1672,"like":5,"dislike":28,"score":-23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T06:57:21.000Z","msg":"撐香港就俾我地無條件移民啦<br />\n得把口有撚用咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38be8698196ebb7f4f68dda3d324f3754a4802bd","tid":1198130,"uid":51701,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T06:58:02.000Z","msg":"lm睇班ive仔asso 仔叫人地台狗"},{"pid":"0cee72774fa3da6637a7b6b79d9c323eeffa183c","tid":1198130,"uid":51701,"like":45,"dislike":1,"score":44,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T07